# Pawrrtal skills

Canonical skills live in `.agent/skills/` (agentic-stack portable brain).
Harness mirrors: `.agents/skills/`, `.claude/skills/`, `.cursor/plugins/pawrrtal/skills/`.

Generated skills: `bun run skill-gen:generate` writes to `.agent/skills/`.
Root `AGENTS.md` is a stub pointing to `.agent/AGENTS.md` (entry contract).
Facts → `memory/semantic/DOMAIN_KNOWLEDGE.md`; taste → `memory/personal/PREFERENCES.md`;
procedures → skills (`repo-operations`, `code-quality`, …). Load `agents-md` before editing.
